CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 5 reads: "3. Minestrone Soup by H. J. Heinz Company was passed out by Marjorie Morgan as representatives Rudy Weber and Robert Hoffman stand by."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including Rudy Weber, Robert Hoffman, and Marjorie Jackson (Keith) or Morgan dishing out samples in Heinz promotional booth in Syria Mosque for the 1958  Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
